***[[Proto-Slavic|Slavic]]: {{lang|sla-x-proto|per(g)ynja}}, 'wooded hills' (perhaps an early borrowing from Germanic),{{Sfn|Jackson|2002|p=75–76}}{{Sfn|West|2007|p=241}}
