*[[Italica|Italic]]:
**[[Italian language|Italian]]: {{lang|it|porca}}, a word meaning 'fir tree' in the Trentino dialect. Mallory and Adams suppose it is a loanword from Raetic.{{Sfn|Mallory|Adams|1997|p=407}}
